Subject: [PATCH] Paper -> Re-add Spigot's hopper-check feature

重新启用 Spigot 的漏斗检测间隔，检测间隔请务必不要使用默认值 8，那太高了，经测试 4 以内比较合适。
Link：https://github.com/PaperMC/Paper/blob/master/Spigot-Server-Patches/0081-Re-add-Spigot-s-hopper-check-feature.patch

diff --git a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/TileEntityHopper.java b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/TileEntityHopper.java
index 7b00f6a..f46be7a 100644
--- a/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/TileEntityHopper.java
+++ b/src/main/java/net/minecraft/server/TileEntityHopper.java
@@ -178,6 +178,7 @@ public class TileEntityHopper extends TileEntityLootable implements IHopper, ITi
                     this.update();
                     return true;
                 }
+                this.setCooldown(world.spigotConfig.hopperCheck);
             }
 
             return false;
